column2: "There are a lot of Darkers. This could be the first time I've seen this amount."
"It's been said for Darkers that where there's one, there's a hundred."
"From about ten years ago up until now, things have been pretty quiet. I wonder what changed exactly."
"They don't talk, there are too many and no one has any idea what they're after yet."
"Frankly speaking they're pretty eerie. It's best not to let our guards down while they're around."
